Description: Nx is a build system, optimized for monorepos
 Nx is a build system, optimized for monorepos, with plugins for popular
 frameworks and tools and advanced CI capabilities including caching and
 distribution.
 .
 Note: Nx requires Node.js 20 or higher for optimal functionality.
 The package will warn if an older version is detected.
